{
  "id": "5ac4bc402630ea0014203612",
  "title": "Adner2002",
  "created": 1522842690,
  "updated": 1525085353,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5ac4bc41aff09e0000d45091",
      "text": "Adner2002",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1522842690,
      "updated": 1522842700
    },
    {
      "id": "5ac4bc42aff09e0000d45092",
      "text": "Adner, R. (2002). When are technologies disruptive? A demand-based view of the emergence of competition. Strategic Management Journal, 23(8), 667–688. http://doi.org/10.1002/smj.246",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1522842690,
      "updated": 1525085353
    },
    {
      "id": "5acaefc8aff09e00007432a1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523249096,
      "updated": 1523249096
    },
    {
      "id": "5ac4bc52aff09e0000d45093",
      "text": "背景の解説",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1522842706,
      "updated": 1523249101
    },
    {
      "id": "5acaefdaaff09e00007432a3",
      "text": "\tこの領域の地図を把握する上で有用そうなので訳しておく",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523249115,
      "updated": 1523249129
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb741caff09e00003eebcc",
      "text": "  [Adner2002による背景説明]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523282973,
      "updated": 1523282973
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb741eaff09e00003eebcd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523282975,
      "updated": 1523282975
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb73fcaff09e00003eebcb",
      "text": "\tこの論文では技術競争に[demand-based view]を導入",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523282940,
      "updated": 1523283032
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb744baff09e00003eebcf",
      "text": " \tマーケットセグメントの選考の間の関係",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523283020,
      "updated": 1523283055
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb746faff09e00003eebd0",
      "text": "  \t[preference overlap]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523283056,
      "updated": 1523283069
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb747daff09e00003eebd2",
      "text": "   [preference symmetry]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523283070,
      "updated": 1523283080
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb749faff09e00003eebd3",
      "text": "  二つのマーケットセグメントの間の境界をblurする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523283103,
      "updated": 1523283113
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb74c8aff09e00003eebd4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523283145,
      "updated": 1523283145
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb7429aff09e00003eebce",
      "text": "\tthreshold",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523282986,
      "updated": 1523283147
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb7505aff09e00003eebd6",
      "text": "  \"critical performance levels that must be met for an offering to become relevant to a decision set\"",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523283205,
      "updated": 1523283224
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb7518aff09e00003eebe0",
      "text": "  これは社会科学の領域でよく知られた概念(Granovetter, 1978; Varian, 1978; David, 1969; McFadden,1986; Meyer and Kahn, 1991)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523283224,
      "updated": 1523283253
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb7534aff09e00003eebe1",
      "text": "  著者らは2種類の閾値を区別",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523283253,
      "updated": 1523283261
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb753daff09e00003eebe2",
      "text": "\t\t\tA consumer’s functional threshold",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523283261,
      "updated": 1523283280
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb7550aff09e00003eebe3",
      "text": "    = minimum level of performance below which a consumer will not accept a product regardless of its price. ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523283280,
      "updated": 1523283373
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb7677aff09e00003eebf3",
      "text": "    各々の顧客が異なった閾値と効用関数を持っていて、選好とはその最大化である。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523283575,
      "updated": 1523283682
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb75acaff09e00003eebe4",
      "text": " \t\t\t(脚注3) この定式化は歴史のある物",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523283373,
      "updated": 1523283681
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb75bdaff09e00003eebe6",
      "text": "    \tThis conceptualization follows a long tradition of work in marketing, decision science, and economics (Griliches, 1961; Lancaster, 1979; Green and Wind, 1973; Trajtenberg, 1990)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523283389,
      "updated": 1523283679
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb75d2aff09e00003eebe9",
      "text": "     \tconsumers have relative preferences for product characteristics",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523283411,
      "updated": 1523283679
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb7613aff09e00003eebf1",
      "text": "      consumer choice can be usefully conceived as the maximization of utility measured in terms of the functional characteristics that are embodied in their product choices. ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523283476,
      "updated": 1523283679
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb762aaff09e00003eebf2",
      "text": "      The treatment of preferences for goods as being derived from preferences for collections of characteristics lies at the heart of established techniques such as [hedonic analysis], [conjoint analysis], and [multidimensional logit models] of brand choice",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523283498,
      "updated": 1523283679
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb75aeaff09e00003eebe5",
      "text": "\t\t\tNet utility threshold",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523283375,
      "updated": 1523283693
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb76edaff09e00003eebf5",
      "text": "   \t価格と顧客のdecision functionの間を取り持つ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523283693,
      "updated": 1523283727
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb770eaff09e00003eebf6",
      "text": "    highest price a consumer will pay for a product that just meets her functional threshold",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523283727,
      "updated": 1523283751
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb77dfaff09e00003eebf8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523283936,
      "updated": 1523283936
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb76edaff09e00003eebf4",
      "text": " value trajectoryは[Cobb-Douglas utility curve]の勾配",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523283693,
      "updated": 1523284644
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb77e2aff09e00003eebf9",
      "text": "  つまり特定の効用を得るうえで機能の総和が最小となる点",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523283939,
      "updated": 1523284683
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb7ad6aff09e000004662f",
      "text": "  [Lancaster]的に言えば",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523284694,
      "updated": 1523284704
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb7b15aff09e0000046630",
      "text": "  \t it is defined by the vector which minimizes the characteristic resources required to attain a given utility level; that is, the vector along which the compensating function is equal to unity (Lancaster, 1979, 1991)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523284757,
      "updated": 1523284768
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb8449aff09e00003eec0a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523287113,
      "updated": 1523287113
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb8449aff09e00003eec0b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523287113,
      "updated": 1523287113
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb8449aff09e00003eec09",
      "text": "\t価格を逆数の形で効用に入れてる (eq.2) まあそりゃそうするよね",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523287113,
      "updated": 1523287317
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb86e0aff09e00003eec0d",
      "text": "\t[$ U = B^a (1/P)^{1-a}]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523287777,
      "updated": 1523287811
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb8505aff09e00003eec0c",
      "text": "\t\tこれは対数を取ると[$ \\log U = a \\log B + (1 - a) \\log (1/P)]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523287301,
      "updated": 1523287893
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb870baff09e00003eec0e",
      "text": "\t\t\t[$ \\log U / (1 - a) = a / (1 - a) \\log B - \\log P]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523287820,
      "updated": 1523287937
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb876eaff09e00003eec0f",
      "text": "\t\tとなるので[$ U = KB - P] となる[Tirole1988]のmonotonic variantである(脚注9)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523287919,
      "updated": 1523287992
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb8784aff09e00003eec10",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523287941,
      "updated": 1523287941
    }
  ]
}